  "instructions_to_main_agent": [
    "1. SETUP: Install 'lucide-react' for icons. Add the Google Fonts link to the index.html head.",
    "2. LANGUAGE CONTEXT: Create a 'LanguageContext' that manages 'lang' (en, fa, ps) and 'dir' (ltr, rtl). Wrap the app in this context.",
    "3. RTL IMPLEMENTATION: When 'dir' is 'rtl', ensure the layout mirrors correctly. Use 'flex-row-reverse' if needed, or rely on 'dir=rtl' native behavior with logical properties.",
    "4. TRANSLATIONS: Create a simple translation dictionary object for all static text (Nav items, Headings, Buttons).",
    "5. ANIMATIONS: Use 'framer-motion' for the Hero Slider and scroll reveal animations for product cards.",
    "6. FORMS: Use Shadcn UI components for the Contact and Inquiry forms. Style them to match the Amber/Stone theme.",
    "7. RESPONSIVENESS: Ensure the mobile menu works correctly in both RTL and LTR modes (drawer should slide from the correct side)."
  ],
